data.title: Buddies!
data.meta_description: Listen to Buddies! on Spotify. Buddies is a Podcast with Comedian Frank Castillo & JP, two avid stoners that educate listeners every week as they take a deep dive into weed culture, Cannabis and Comedy. With a mix of fun segments, they will educate listeners about legislation, who’s growing best weed on the market, and interview some fun guests.  Kissing In A Milkshake is a podcast with the Castillo’s! Hannah Jane Castillo a therapist and Frank Castillo a comedian. He tries to make her laugh while she tries to figure out what’s wrong with him.
